title: Bob Dylan & other artists Duets Volume 3 & 4
description:
Bob Dylan & Others Duets Vol 3&4

This a collection made out of love for the music of Bob Dylan. During his career he did have fruitful interacions with 
lots of other musicians. The duets volumes gives examaples of this interaction through the years, starting in 1958.
The soundquality does vary and specialy the early recordings are sometimes not very well to the standards of today!
But still nice to hear.
